name: Association of Future Student Affairs Professionals
description: The organization is affiliated with the Student Affairs Administration in Higher Education (SAAHE) academic program and serves as a resource for faculty, staff and students involved in the program. In addition, we strive to create professional and social development opportunities for our current members and aid in the recruitment of potential SAAHE students. Furthermore, although this organization is affiliated with the SAAHE academic program, it is a recognized student organization and its members are entitled to all associated privileges.
